Package: gmbaR
Type: Package
Title: A set of R functions to work with the GMBA Inventory v2.0
Version: 0.1.0
Author: c(person("Jonas", "Geschke", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "jonas.geschke@ips.unibe.ch", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5654-9313")),
